        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This isn't another generic e-signature tool collecting dust in your browser bookmarks. SignNow is a full document workflow platform that handles everything from simple signature requests to complex multi-step contract automation. And it does it without making you feel like you need a computer science degree.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Let me walk you through exactly why this tool has earned a permanent spot in my daily workflow — and why it might do the same for yours.",
