          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've used DocuSign, HelloSign, PandaDoc, and Adobe Sign. They're all fine tools. But SignNow consistently wins on three fronts that matter most to me: speed, simplicity, and cost.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Speed That Actually Impresses",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Sending a document for signature takes under 60 seconds. I'm not exaggerating. Upload a PDF, drag signature fields where you need them, add your recipient's email, and hit send. Done.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The signing experience on the recipient's end is equally frictionless. They click a link, draw or type their signature, and the document is instantly returned to you. No account creation required. No confusing navigation. No \"please download our app first.\"",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Simplicity Without Sacrificing Power",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's where SignNow really shines. The interface is clean enough that my 62-year-old father successfully signed a contract on his first try — without me walking him through it. Yet the platform is powerful enough to handle conditional logic in forms, multi-party signing sequences, and automated reminders.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You get the rare combination of a tool that's easy to start with and deep enough to grow into.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Pricing That Respects Your Budget",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Let's talk numbers. SignNow's Business plan starts at $10 per month when billed annually. That's for unlimited users — yes, unlimited. Compare that to competitors charging $15-25 per user per month, and the math speaks for itself.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For a team of 10 people, you're looking at $10/month total with SignNow versus $150-250/month elsewhere. Over a year, that's a difference of $1,680 to $2,880. For a startup or growing business, that's real money.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
