          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You can now build dynamic templates that auto-populate with data from your CRM, form responses, or API calls. Imagine sending 50 personalized contracts in the time it used to take to send one. That's not hypothetical — I did this last month for a client onboarding sprint.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Advanced Workflow Builder",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The visual workflow editor lets you map out multi-step approval chains with conditional branching. If a contract value exceeds $10,000, route it to the VP. If it's under that threshold, send it straight to the client. No coding. No Zapier workarounds. Just drag, drop, and configure.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Mobile App Overhaul",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The updated SignNow app for iOS and Android now supports offline signing, biometric authentication, and real-time document tracking. I've had clients sign contracts while sitting in airport lounges with spotty Wi-Fi. The offline mode saved the deal.",
            "marks": []
          }
