          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Shared document libraries, team-level permission settings, and centralized audit trails make it easy for multiple departments to use SignNow without stepping on each other's toes. Sales, legal, and HR can all operate from the same platform with separate workflows and access levels.",
