      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you're sending contracts, proposals, or invoices that need signatures, SignNow eliminates the back-and-forth email dance. I've watched freelancers cut their contract turnaround time from 3 days to 3 hours. At $10/month with unlimited users, the ROI is immediate.",
            "marks": []
