      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "SignNow accelerates deal closures. Period. Sales reps can send quotes and agreements directly from their CRM, track when documents are opened, and trigger automated follow-ups. No more \"I never received that contract\" excuses.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "A mid-sized SaaS company I consulted with reduced their average deal-close time by 40% after switching to SignNow. They attribute it directly to the frictionless signing experience and real-time notifications.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "HR & People Operations",
