          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Onboarding paperwork is one of the most tedious parts of hiring. SignNow lets HR teams send offer letters, NDAs, tax forms, and policy acknowledgments in a single automated bundle. New hires can sign everything from their phone before day one.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Legal & Compliance Teams",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Every signature comes with a detailed audit trail — IP addresses, timestamps, authentication methods. SignNow is compliant with ESIGN, UETA, eIDAS, HIPAA, SOC 2 Type II, and GDPR. For regulated industries, this isn't a nice-to-have. It's mandatory.",
            "marks": []
