        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Real Estate Professionals",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Lease agreements, purchase contracts, disclosure forms — real estate runs on paper (or it used to). Agents using SignNow report closing deals faster because clients can sign from anywhere, on any device, at any hour.",
