            "text": "Yes. SignNow's electronic signatures are legally binding and compliant with ESIGN, UETA, eIDAS, and other international e-signature laws. Each signature includes a comprehensive audit trail with timestamps, IP addresses, and authentication details that hold up in legal proceedings.",
            "marks": []
